{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "These are not good people you want to wave to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I, I will never forget that particular scene, how I was waving to the Germans and saying to myself, I'm nuts.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I shouldn't be waving to, to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's the enemy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yeah, that's, that's, that's how I remember the first Germans coming to, to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Never did, never did-- the only thing was that I think children pick up the underlying fear from their parents immediately.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A little child will starts-- will start to cry when a mother starts to cry.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It seems to transfer itself automatically.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think children, of course, are very sensitive to, also to vibrations in the air.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in, in this case, I was picking up the vibrations in the air, and said, oh boy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We are in deep trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then my father started to explain to me that we may have to go into hiding or underground from the, from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because they were-- and he said, when I was in Germany, and he had lived for many years in Germany, and he spoke fluent German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He spoke so good German that, German that he could pass for German, as a matter of fact.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He, he said, well, he said, this is going the wrong way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We are going to be in, in big difficulties.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And like, he bought a lot of food when the war broke out, like a lot of people did in Amsterdam, or all over, to cover themselves in case of shortages.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I still don't care that much for tomato soup with rice because of the hundreds of cans of tomato soup and rice we had.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I, I felt thoroughly, completely, that this was difficult times.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I knew we were at war.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
